records.name: Filitheyo Island Resort

descriptions.direction: Located in Filitheyo, Filitheyo Island Resort is on the beach. Local points of interest include Meedhuffushi Island Beach, Meedhuffushi Island Pier, and Meedhoo Harbour. With snorkeling, water skiing, and windsurfing nearby, you'll find plenty of adventures in the water.
descriptions.general: General description: In the vicinity of the hotel´s own beach is situated the hotel Filitheyo Island Resort. The town Male is around 120 km away. The airport (MLE) is approx. 125 km away. The hotel and airport are linked by a shuttle (for a fee). Amenities: The resort has 125 rooms. It is equipped with a 24h reception (check-in from 14:00, check-out until 12:00), a lobby with bar, a safe (where applicable, for a fee), a shop as well as a money changing facility. For the meals, there are two restaurants. For guests with physical disabilities the hotel has a barrier-free access. For the laundry / ironing service the hotel charges a fee (where applicable). Pool: In the outdoor area of the hotel you will find a children´s pool. Here, there are sun loungers and sun umbrellas where applicable, for a fee available. Meals: Breakfast from the buffet. Sport and Leisure: Sports and entertainment: Billiards (where applicable, for a fee), darts (where applicable, for a fee), table tennis (where applicable, for a fee) and fitness. Spa area and massages available (where applicable for a fee). Child supervision: babysitting (where applicable, for a fee). Additional information: Additional fees may apply for certain facilities, amenities or activities. Some services depend on the local climatic conditions and the season. Languages spoken: English. FamilyVilla (Seaplane Included): With shared pool, kettle (where applicable, for a fee) and safe (where applicable, for a fee) as well as centrally controlled air conditioning. Bathroom with bathtub and shower. Deluxe Villa (Seaplane Included): With shared pool, kettle (where applicable, for a fee) and safe (where applicable, for a fee) as well as centrally controlled air conditioning. Bathroom with bathtub and shower. Superior Villa (Seaplane Included): With shared pool, kettle (where applicable, for a fee) and safe (where applicable, for a fee) as well as centrally controlled air conditioning. Bathroom with bathtub and shower. Superior Villa (Seaplane Promotion): With shared pool, kettle (where applicable, for a fee) and safe (where applicable, for a fee) as well as centrally controlled air conditioning. Bathroom with bathtub and shower. Water Villa (Seaplane Included): With shared pool, kettle (where applicable, for a fee) and safe (where applicable, for a fee) as well as centrally controlled air conditioning. Bathroom with bathtub and shower. Transfer options mandatory for all the guests. Seaplane transfers are applicable to all guests arriving at Male Airport between 06:30 to 15:00 hrs. Approx of 35 mins away from Male Airport to Resort. Available during daylight hours from 6:30 hrs to 16:00 hrs.Last international arrival flight for seaplane connection is 15:00h. USD6 - will be charged for infant per day Standard permissible weight is 25 kg, which includes 20 kg of luggage per person.
